title: Honey-Glazed Garlic Pork & Cheesy Roast Veggie Toss with Chargrilled Capsicum Yoghurt
description: Allow us to take you on a culinary escapade and savour the flavours of the Mediterranean with this delectable dish. Juicy pork is perfectly cooked in our herby mushroom seasoning, with a drizzle of honey for a touch of sweetness. A medley of roasted veggies and a tangy sauce drizzled over the top complete this perfect meal!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
